# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [v0.1.1] - 2026-06-14

### Added

- Simple remove rule like "./netvanguard-cli remove-rule 1" removed index 1

### Fixed

- Change reply format with bit mask, remove redundancy

## [v0.1.0] - 2026-06-13

### Added

- Kernel-netfilter module with Netfilter hook integration
- CLI tools for rule addition and deletion
- Radix tree-based index database for efficient rule storage
- Test suite covering netlink and TCP socket communication
- Generic netlink API for user-kernel space IPC
- Pre-routing and post-routing Netfilter hooks

[v0.1.0]: https://github.com/yousefsmt/NetVanguard/tree/v0.1.0
[v0.1.1]: https://github.com/yousefsmt/NetVanguard/tree/v0.1.1